data.description: SELLER IS MOTIVATED! ''The house don't fall when the bones are good'' Pride of ownership definitely shows on this home built in 1954! Located in the heart of Pleasure Ridge Park in Louisville. This oversized corner lot offers plenty of space for entertaining and SO much more. The impeccable curb appeal and beautiful character of this property features original natural hardwood floors and trim throughout. Within the last 3 years there have been IMPROVEMENTS GALORE! Such as, full kitchen update, HVAC system, complete window replacement, basement waterproofing, water heater, installation of a 33 ft. above ground swimming pool just to name a few. Make sure to check out the Disclosures and Improvements list for full details of how this home has been meticulously cared for.
